    "multi_query": true,
    "algorithm_path": "comprehensive",
    "algorithm_path_description": "Union of HCV dx codes, DAA Rx, and HCV antibody labs. Tests provider-level identification for screening/treatment cascade. The DAA query has minimal Path C overcount — like MS DMTs, DAAs are HCV-specific.",
